<A>__{as it circles the anti like figures of workers (s) the great ship dwarfs everything. the drydock becomes a fragile filigree framing the ship's great curved bulk. the tiny pod continues to move along it. small automated welding devices move along the gird ers, working with brief, bright orange white flares. in other areas of metal lace structure, supplies and equipment are being loaded onto the ship. the pod continues moving (scott is giving kirk time to see all), watched carefully by the tiny figures of supervising technicians on the drydock. now the pod moves toward mating position. it closes in, secures itself to the outer airlock.}
